      <title>不论好坏，全球债券市场动荡都未波及欧元区</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/good-reasons-bad-global-bond-wobble-passes-over-euro-zone-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在英国和美国面临投资者担心债务增长和通胀居高不下的压力之际，欧元区似乎基本逃脱了市场的愤怒——尽管这种平静背后的原因并不全是令人愉快的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/good-reasons-bad-global-bond-wobble-passes-over-euro-zone-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 15:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
